        hello and welcome to my website.
        FIRST is an international organization that inspires young people to become leaders in science and technology. It combines robotics, engineering, and programming with teamwork and creativity. Students in FIRST work together to design, build, and code robots to complete challenges. The program emphasizes learning through hands-on experience rather than just theory. FIRST also promotes important values such as cooperation, respect, and problem solving. Participants develop technical skills in coding, mechanics, and electronics. Beyond technology, students gain confidence and communication skills. Competitions encourage innovation while fostering a friendly and supportive environment. FIRST prepares students for future careers in STEM fields. Overall, FIRST helps turn curiosity into real-world skills and inspiration.
